flowchart LR
  subgraph ClientUI[Client/UI]
    UI[jarvis-frontend (assumption)]
  end

  subgraph Backend[Backend]
    JBE[jarvis-backend (HTTP+WS)]
    ROUTE[agent routing (main.py)]
  end

  subgraph MCPTools[MCP/Tools]
    MCP[mcp-bundle (1MCP gateway)]
  end

  subgraph Workers[Workers]
    DRW[deep-research-worker (HTTP)]
  end

  subgraph AuthSecrets[Auth/Secrets (env vars)]
    SECRETS[env vars / tokens / OAuth]
  end

  subgraph DataStores[Data Stores]
    JSQL[sqlite (jarvis sessions)]
    DSQL[sqlite (deep research)]
    WV[weaviate]
  end

  subgraph ExternalServices[External Services]
    GEM[Gemini API]
    GAPIS[Google APIs]
    GS[Google Sheets]
    GH[GitHub API]
    PORT[Portainer API]
  end

  UI -->|WS /ws/live| JBE
  UI -->|HTTP /health, /openapi.json| JBE

  JBE -->|route/dispatch| ROUTE
  ROUTE -->|LLM API calls| GEM
  ROUTE -->|tool calls| MCP

  JBE -->|HTTP calls| DRW

  JBE -->|SQLite (JARVIS_SESSION_DB)| JSQL
  DRW -->|SQLite (DEEP_RESEARCH_DB)| DSQL
  JBE -->|retrieval/index (WEAVIATE_URL)| WV

  MCP -->|tool calls (OAuth)| GAPIS
  JBE -->|memory read/write| GS
  JBE -->|API calls (token RO/RW)| GH
  JBE -->|API calls| PORT

  JBE -.->|reads secrets| SECRETS
  MCP -.->|reads secrets| SECRETS
